grade_preconditions.en:
To be eligible to write the final exam, you must,
(1) score 42/84 (altogether) on Tests 1 and 2 and Quizzes 1  to 7;
(2) must also write at least 5 Quizzes;
(3) attend 90% of the lectures.
(4) Test 3 and Quiz 8 do not count towards the eligibility for writing the final exam.

